-- Labigel Cafe menu seed data (categories, subcategories, products).
--
-- The application code does NOT seed real menu content — DataInitializer
-- only creates a default admin user and a blank site_settings row. This
-- file restores the actual menu that was built via the admin panel.
--
-- Usage (after `docker compose up -d` has created the schema at least once):
--   docker exec -i labigel_db psql -U labigel -d labigel_db < labigel-backend/db/seed_data.sql
--
-- Safe to re-run only on an EMPTY categories/subcategories/products set —
-- it will fail on duplicate primary keys/slugs if run twice.
--
